# manga-downloader overview

Node.js 18+ CLI (ESM, no build). Package manager: **pnpm**.

## Layout

- `bin/manga-downloader.js` — CLI entry
- `plugins/<id>/index.js` — source plugins (auto-discovered)
- `plugins/centralnovel/` — reference implementation
- `lib/` — core (config, download, output, commands)
- `tests/` — `node --test` + fixtures

Read [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) and [docs/](docs/) for full context.

## Rules

- Run `pnpm test` after code changes
- Never commit `config.json`
- `plugin.id` must match folder name under `plugins/`
- Site-specific logic stays in `plugins/` — not in `lib/`
- CLI user messages in Portuguese; dev docs in English
- Minimal diffs — follow existing conventions
